title: Trump's wall could cost $21.6 BILLION and take until 2020
text: Trump's border wall might not be done until the end of 2020 and could cost $21.6 BILLION â€“ nearly twice what he claimed during campaign Trump's 'wall' could actually be a series of wall segments and fences Homeland Security report leaked to Reuters shows a potential $21.6 billion cost The president estimated a $12 billion price tag during his campaign Trump has ordered the start of construction and said Thursday that designs are already underway But the DHS report says building the wall could take until the end of 2020 Published: 11:00 GMT, 10 February 2017 | Updated: 14:15 GMT, 10 February 2017 5 shares
